Argeta Pate made from the best tuna.

No artificial colors
Gluten free

fields.name: Cappy Orange Juice

100% Orange juice. 
Made from pure squeezed oranges and not from concentrate
No added sugar.

fields.name: Banja Luka Cevapcici
fields.description:
Made from the original Banja Luka recipe, these cevapcici will tingle your taste buds. 
Made from 100% port meat

fields.name: Tea Pate
fields.description:
The Gavrilovic tea pate is a popular breakfast spread.
This one has a bit of a kick.

fields.name: Jadro Biscuits
fields.description:
Jadro biscuits are famous in Croatia. 
This is their new coconut and chocolate flavor ready to be enjoyed by the whole family.

fields.name: Jamnica
fields.description: The most refreshing sparkling water you will ever taste. It comes from the deepest springs and is naturally carbonated.

fields.name: Jana Ice Tea
fields.description: Jana is the biggest brand of bottled water in Croatia and their Ice Tea is better than anything you have ever tasted. Add it to your cart and give it a try.

fields.name: Cake Base
fields.description:
So you want to bake a cake? 
Why slave over a stove when you can get everything already made by the best bakers in the country. 
Just add your toppings and you're golden!

fields.name: Biscotti
fields.description:
Are you making tiramisu? Maybe a little peckish and have a sweet tooth? 
You need to have some biscotti around at all times and give in to those cravings.

fields.name: Cevapcici - Sarajevo
fields.description:
They go by many names, but cevapcici are not just a local delicacy in Bosnia, Croatia, Serbia, etc. 
They are a way of life. When you're sad, have cevapi, when you're happy, have cevapi, when you're bored, have cevapi... 
Just have cevapi.

fields.name: Smoked Meat
fields.description:
It's just generic smoked meat. If you don't have any at home, you better get some. 
You never know when your 4th cousins will pop in for visit from Canada.

fields.name: Sudjuk - mild
fields.description: It tastes amazing! But even if you don't like the taste, the smell of this sausage will take you back to the time when your grandma though you were just skin and bones and force fed it to you.

fields.name: Dukatela
fields.description: An essential part of a full Croatian breakfast. It's not Philadelphia, it's better.

fields.name: Cappuccino
fields.description:
There is nothing more Croatian than spending 4 hours in a local cafe sipping one cup of coffee. 
Now, you can do that at home too.

fields.name: Turkish Coffee
fields.description: Espresso not strong enough? No problem, Francks Turkish coffee will have you wired till next week.

fields.name: Camomile Tea
fields.description: Ubiquitous in every Croatian pantry, this is the cure for everything.

fields.name: Forest berry tea
fields.description: A tea with light flavours of forest berries. You will forget where you are and be whisked away to a calm and quiet forest.

fields.name: Chicken Pate
fields.description: Made from the best quality chicken Gavrilovic Chicken Pate is everyone's favorite breakfast.

fields.name: Ham with black currant
fields.description: Canned ham of the finest quality.

fields.name: Hot Dogs in salty brine
fields.description: Preppers delight.

fields.name: Spicy Pate
fields.description:
Infused with chilli peppers and black pepper corns, this pate is a must try. 
Made from the best quality ingredients, it is a delicacy.

fields.name: Budjola
fields.description: Budjola is smoked pork neck and is a delicacy claimed by both Croatia and Italy.

fields.name: Toast Cracker
fields.description: A pre toasted toast. For the long commute.

fields.name: Somun Bread
fields.description: Somun bread is essential for the best cevapi experience.

fields.name: Polenta
fields.description: A great accompaniment to pork or beef dishes.

fields.name: Macarons
fields.description: Great pasta for mac & cheese or as noodles in stew.

fields.name: Spaghetti
fields.description: Made from the best durum wheat, these should be your no. 1 choice.

fields.name: Bajadera
fields.description:
The most iconic chocolate box to come out of Kras. 
Hazel fudge between two slabs of Nutella like chocolate.

fields.name: Dorina Rice
fields.description: Milk chocolate with rice. Great taste with half the calories.
